00:36:11.118 --> 00:36:11.983
constraints.

00:36:11.983 --> 00:36:13.650
The original budget
constraint continues

00:36:13.650 --> 00:36:17.940
to be the original budget line
running from 5,000 to 5,000.

00:36:17.940 --> 00:36:20.850
The new budget constraint
is this kinked line

00:36:20.850 --> 00:36:25.230
that runs from 5,000 on
the y-axis to the point

00:36:25.230 --> 00:36:29.680
x2 at 5,000 on the y-axis.

00:36:29.680 --> 00:36:32.770
So it starts at 5,000 on
the y-axis, 0 on the x-axis.

00:36:32.770 --> 00:36:35.900
There's a flat line that goes
to 5,000 on the y-axis, 500

00:36:35.900 --> 00:36:37.048
on the x-axis.

00:36:37.048 --> 00:36:39.340
And then it slopes down
