00:37:47.265 --> 00:37:48.140
That's exactly right.

00:37:48.140 --> 00:37:50.980
So, for person y,
there's no difference.

00:37:50.980 --> 00:37:54.378
Look, they're already
spending, what, $4,900 on food.

00:37:54.378 --> 00:37:56.170
