00:38:01.270 --> 00:38:02.010
in cash.

00:38:02.010 --> 00:38:02.980
They're indifferent.

00:38:02.980 --> 00:38:04.460
So nothing affects them.

00:38:04.460 --> 00:38:07.920
But what about person x?

00:38:07.920 --> 00:38:11.470
Well, person x, remember,
