00:42:08.190 --> 00:42:11.070
If tax-- why am I giving
money to this poor guy?

00:42:11.070 --> 00:42:13.300
Because I'm sad his poor.

00:42:13.300 --> 00:42:15.940
But, what you're saying, I'm
not actually that sad he's poor.

00:42:15.940 --> 00:42:17.930
I'm sad he's not eating.

00:42:17.930 --> 00:42:19.760
If you're really
just sad he's poor,

