then you should give him money.

00:42:21.230 --> 00:42:22.820
If what you're
sad about is, gee,

00:42:22.820 --> 00:42:23.810
I don't like how he's living--

00:42:23.810 --> 00:42:24.300
I don't like his--

00:42:24.300 --> 00:42:26.910
I'm sad he can't have better
