00:42:26.910 --> 00:42:27.410
he lives.

00:42:27.410 --> 00:42:29.540
Then you're starting to
impose your preferences,

00:42:29.540 --> 00:42:30.498
but let's be important.

00:42:30.498 --> 00:42:32.876
That's imposing
your preferences.

00:42:32.876 --> 00:42:33.548
Yeah?

00:42:33.548 --> 00:42:35.590
AUDIENCE: I feel like the
