00:43:02.510 --> 00:43:05.430
you should give them cash, OK?

00:43:05.430 --> 00:43:10.410
So that raises
two questions, OK?

00:43:10.410 --> 00:43:14.760
First of all, first
question-- yeah?

00:43:14.760 --> 00:43:17.035
AUDIENCE: So how about
like negative [INAUDIBLE]..

